HEADWORD: Snobbish
<hw>Snob"bish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
a snob; characteristic of, or befitting, a snob; vulgarly
pretentious.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Snob"bish*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

